NG0711:1: bum pa brum las gzhal yas su //
NG0711:2: bam las 'o ma'i rgya mtsho bskyed //
NG0711:3: dbus su pam las pad+ma dang *//
NG0711:4: nyi zla'i gdan la hum las ni //
NG0711:5: rdo rje gtum po bskyed byas la //
NG0711:6: mchod bstim rgyas gdab dbang bskur nas //
NG0711:7: bum pa'i lha la dmigs byas la //
NG0711:8: ye ge bcu pa brgya rtsa brgyad //
NG0711:9: bzlas la byin gyis brlab par bya //
NG0711:10: las kyi bum pa shar trang gzhag / rdo rje chu ru bsams pas brlab //
NG0711:11: dbang rdzas rnams kyang rim par brlab //
NG0711:12: mchod pa dang ni gtor ma bsham //
NG0711:13: de nas mtshams gcad mchod pa brlab //
NG0711:14: ting 'dzin gsum las dbang chen dang *//
NG0711:16: gzhal yas bsam las lha bskyed nas //
NG0711:17: spyan drangs mchod bzlas la sogs pas //
NG0711:18: ye shes lha rnams mnyes par bsnyen //
NG0711:19: de nas slob mas bla ma yis //
NG0711:20: rjes su 'breng la tshig brjod de //
NG0711:21: bu yis dbang bskur gsol ba gdab //
NG0711:22: de nas rdo rje slob dpon gyis //
NG0711:23: mdun du slob ma gnas pa de //
NG0711:24: shu n+ya ta yis stong par bsgom //
NG0711:25: de las sems nyid hum du bsgom //
NG0711:26: de las rdo rje de las sku //
NG0711:27: spro bsdu byas la gtum por bskyed //
NG0711:28: bdag gi thugs kha'i hum las ni //
NG0711:29: ye shes phyag rdor spyan drangs bstim //
NG0711:30: de la thugs kha'i lha mos mchod //
NG0711:31: de nas slob pa'i spyo bo ru //
NG0711:32: yi ge om bsams 'phros pa yis //
NG0711:33: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku mnyes nas //
NG0711:34: slar 'dus slob ma'i spyi bor thim //
NG0711:35: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku yi dbang *//
NG0711:36: byin rlabs bsdus la bstim par bya //
NG0711:37: om sarba ta tha ga ta ka ya badzra swa b+ha ba ad ma ko\u0f85ham //
NG0711:40: sku yi dbang dang byin brlabs ni //
NG0711:41: thob par bsam la dbang rtags ni //
NG0711:42: spyi bor om la sngags bskor bsam //
NG0711:43: ba spu'i bu ga'i khro bo dang *//
NG0711:44: rdo rje go cha gtams pa las //
NG0711:45: ye shes me dpung 'bar ba bsam //
NG0711:46: de nas de yi mgrin par ni //
NG0711:47: ye ge am bsams de 'phros pas //
NG0711:48: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung 'phros pas //
NG0711:49: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung mnyes nas //
NG0711:50: slar 'dus dbang dang byin bsdus te //
NG0711:51: slob ma'i mgrin par thim pa yis //
NG0711:52: sangs rgyas rnams kyi gsung gi dbang *//
NG0711:53: byin bsdus de la thim par bsam //
NG0711:54: om sarba ta tha ga ta ba ka badzra swa b+ha ba at+ma ko\u0f85 ham /
NG0711:57: dbang dang byin brlabs rtags nyid ni //
NG0711:58: ljags ni rdo rje rtse lnga pa //
NG0711:59: sngags kyi zar bus mtshon par bsam //
NG0711:60: de nas slob ma'i snying kha ru //
NG0711:61: yi ge hum bsam de nyid las //
NG0711:63: thugs kyi dbang dang byin brlab kun //
NG0711:64: bsdus nas thugs khar thim par bsam //
NG0711:65: om sarba ta tha ga ta tsit+ta badzra swab+ha ba at+ma ko \u0f85ham /
NG0711:68: dbang rtags snying nyid pad+mar gyur //
NG0711:69: de las rdo rje sbag byas te //
NG0711:72: nyi zla'i steng na ye shes sems //
NG0711:73: de yi thugs khar rdo rje yis //
NG0711:74: lte bar hum las sngags bskor bsam //
NG0711:75: de nas bum pa'i dbang bskur pas //
NG0711:76: chos dbyings dag pa'i bum pa na //
NG0711:77: ye shes gsang bdag rdo rje bzhugs //
NG0711:78: spyi nas bstim zhing dbang bskur bas //
NG0711:79: lus la rdo rje bltam par shog / om tsan+da
NG0711:80: maha ro sha na badzra ka sha a b+hi shany+tsa
NG0711:81: a / de nas dbu rgyan gyi dbang bskur ba //
NG0711:82: sku dang ye shes dbu rgyan 'di //
NG0711:83: sangs rgyas gtsug gi nor bu can //
NG0711:84: ye shes lnga ldan dbu rgyan 'dis //
NG0711:85: khyod la dbang mchog bskur bar bya //
NG0711:86: om tsan+da ma ha ro sha na hum om swa am ham /
NG0711:87: badzra d+ha du ra du na /
NG0711:89: ka ya lba ka tsit+ta gu na kar ma ab+hi shany+tsa a /
NG0711:90: de nas cod pan gyi dbang bskur ba //
NG0711:91: bag chags nyes pa'i skyon bral zhing *//
NG0711:92: 'khor ba'i nyes pas mi gos pa'i //
NG0711:94: khyod la dbang mchog bskur bar bya'o //
NG0711:95: om badzra pa ta lam pa na a b+hi shi ny+tsa a /
NG0711:96: de nas me tog 'phreng ba'i dbang *//
NG0711:99: bsam pa yid bzhin 'grub pa dang *//
NG0711:100: bar chad med par dbang bskur bya'o //
NG0711:101: om badzra radan ma le a b+hi shany+tsa a /
NG0711:102: de nas rdo rje dril bu'i dbang *//
NG0711:103: nyon mongs 'joms pa'i rdo rje dang *//
NG0711:104: chos sgra sgrog pa'i dril bu 'di //
NG0711:105: di ring khyed la dbang bskur bas //
NG0711:106: thabs dang shes rab 'brel bar shog / badzra ga na d+ha a b+hi shany+tsa a /
NG0711:107: de nas mdzad spyod dbang bskur bas //
NG0711:108: bcom ldan rdo rje gtum po ni //
NG0711:109: dus gsum sangs rgyas dbang bskur ba'i //
NG0711:110: sku gsung thugs kyi 'phrin las kyis //
NG0711:111: mdzad spyod rol pa thams cad kyang *//
NG0711:112: di ring khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NG0711:113: thams cad ma lus thob par shog / om tsan+da
NG0711:114: ma ha ro sha na ka ya wa ka tsit+ta
NG0711:116: de nas lcags kyi rdo rjes dbang bskur ba //
NG0711:117: bstan pa'i gtso bo shaka thub kyis //
NG0711:118: lcags kyi rdo rje rtse lnga pa //
NG0711:119: gtad pas gtum po bkra shis bzhi //
NG0711:120: lcags kyi rdo rje dbang thob shog / badzra a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NG0711:121: gser gyi rdo rje dbang bskur bas //
NG0711:122: sangs rgyas rnam par snang mdzad kyi //
NG0711:123: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed gnas nyid du //
NG0711:124: gser gyi rdo rje gsang bdag la //
NG0711:125: dbang bskur bzhin du bkra shis shog / hum badzra b+hi shany+tsa a /
NG0711:126: ye shes rdo rje rtse lnga yis dbang bskur ba //
NG0711:127: sangs rgyas mi bskyod la sogs kyis //
NG0711:128: ye shes rdo rje rtse lnga yis //
NG0711:129: gtum po nyid la dbang bskur bzhin //
NG0711:130: khyod la dbang bskur bkra shis shog / badzra dz+nyan a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NG0711:131: de nas sbrul rgyan gyi dbang bskur ba //
NG0711:132: rgyal mchog dam pa gdags pa'i don //
NG0711:133: klu brgyad rigs bzhir 'dus pas na //
NG0711:134: sbrul rgyan 'di yis dbang bskur bas //
NG0711:135: klu gnyen 'dul ba'i dbang thob shog / badzra na ga a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NG0711:138: chos nyid mi 'gyur na bza' sngo //
NG0711:139: sku la gsol nas bde chen don //
NG0711:140: khyod la di ring dbang bskur bas //
NG0711:141: na bza' rgyan gyi dbang thob shog / badzra rak+sha a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NG0711:142: stag gi sham thabs kyi dbang bskur ba //
NG0711:143: dpa' brtul stag gi sham thabs ni //
NG0711:144: gdul ka ma lus btul ba dang *//
NG0711:146: de bzhin khyod kyis dbang thob shog / bya g+h+ri tsa ra a b+hi shany+tsa a /
NG0711:147: ye shes me dpung gi dbang bskur ba //
NG0711:148: ye shes me dpung nyon mongs bag chags sreg / sku la 'phros pas gdug pa thams cad 'jom //
NG0711:149: di ring khyod la ye shes me dpung dbang bskur bas //
NG0711:150: gdug pa nyon mongs bsreg cing dbang thob shog / badzra dz+wa la ram ram a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NG0711:151: de nas grub na bkra shis lha mo'i dbang bskur ba bya //
NG0711:152: de ltar dbang gi bskur dus su //
NG0711:153: rdzas dang tshig brjod phyi yi dbang *//
NG0711:154: de dus sngags brjod nang gi dbang *//
NG0711:155: ting 'dzin gsal ba gsang ba'i dbang *//
NG0711:156: phyag na rdo rje'i mdzad spyod rnams //
NG0711:157: rang gi sems su ngo sprad la //
NG0711:158: sems nyid gnyis med stong gsal du //
NG0711:159: thag chod ngo sprod rjes gnang sbyin //
NG0711:160: mthar thug pa yi dbang du gsungs //
NG0711:161: de nas slob mas bla ma la //
NG0711:162: yon dbul des na dbang mchog thob //
NG0711:163: bkra shis glu bro gtor ma gtang *//
NG0711:164: dkyil 'khor bsdu zhing rgyun ting bsgom //
NG0711:165: sa tshon gtsang sar dor bar bya //
NG0711:166: bum chu lhag ma btung bar bya //
NG0711:168: rdo rje gtum po dbang bskur ba man ngag gsang ba'i rgyud las //
NG0711:169: dbang bskur ba'i le'u ste drug pa'o //    // de nas rdo rje gtum po yis //
NG0711:170: bdud rtsi 'khyil la bka' stsal pa //
NG0711:171: rten la rab gnas byed 'dod na //
NG0711:173: sngon du bsnyen pa 'bum song nas //
NG0711:174: gnas der khri ni bshams par bya //
NG0711:175: rten rnams shar du zhal bstan la //
NG0711:176: bgegs bskrad khrus bya gu gul bdug / dang po sa gzhi gzung bar bya //
NG0711:177: gnyis pa sta gon bya ba yang *//
NG0711:178: mchod gtor bshams la dkon mchog dang *//
NG0711:179: gtum po nyid la dbul ba dang *//
NG0711:180: chos skyong rnams la gtor ma dbul //
NG0711:181: rten rnams sku ni rnam snang bskyed //
NG0711:182: glegs bam yum mam rdo rje chos //
NG0711:183: thugs rten rdo rje sems dpar bskyed //
NG0711:184: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad dang *//
NG0711:185: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs rnams kun //
NG0711:186: rten la sngon gyi thugs dam bzhin //
NG0711:187: byon par mdzad du gsol brjod pas //
NG0711:188: rang rang gzugs su byon par bsam //
NG0711:189: de la mchod dbul gtor ma gtang *//
NG0711:190: de la gshegs su gsol nas ni //
NG0711:191: de bzhin nub ni tha ma la //
NG0711:192: dngos gzhi sngar ltar bskyed byas la //
NG0711:193: spyan drangs mchod nas thim par bsam //
NG0711:194: om ye d+harma he du pra b+ha ba he tun
NG0711:195: te shan+ta tha ga to h+ya ba dad te shany+tsa
NG0711:196: yo ni ro d+ha e bam pa di ma ha
NG0711:197: shra ma na ye swa ha /
NG0711:199: pa bzlas la gtor bar bya //
NG0711:200: chos sku la ni chos sku yis //
NG0711:201: gzugs brnyan thim par rab gnas bya //
NG0711:202: bkra shis rdzas brgyad dbang yang bskur //
NG0711:203: de nas mchod pa rtsi grub bya //
NG0711:204: 'khor ba ma stongs bar du yang *//
NG0711:205: bzhugs nas 'gro don mdzad par bsam //
NG0711:206: gtor ma cho gas gtang byas la //
NG0711:207: bkra shis glu bro sna tshogs bya //
NG0711:208: gong du gtum po'i bsnyen pa bya //
NG0711:209: rten 'brel snying po khri bzlas la //
NG0711:210: me tog las ni dmigs la'o //
NG0711:211: dkyil 'khor bsdu zhing dge bar bsngo //
NG0711:213: rdo rje gtum po man ngag gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NG0711:214: rab tu gnas pa'i le'u ste bdun pa'o ///
NG0711:215: / de nas yang dag bshad bya ba //
NG0711:216: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa yang nyon cig / dbang thob mdzes pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NG0711:217: dam tshig dam la nan tan bsrung *//
NG0711:218: rtsa ba sku gsung thugs dang ni //
NG0711:219: yan lag byang chub sems kyi ni //
NG0711:220: dam tshig bsrung na dbang de 'chags //
NG0711:221: byin brlabs dngos grub dpag med 'byung *//
NG0711:223: phyi ma rdo rje'i gral du 'gro //
NG0711:224: rdo rje gtum po'i 'phrin las ni //
NG0711:225: zhi ba dang ni rgyas pa dang *//
NG0711:226: dbang dang mngon spyod bsrung gso dang *//
NG0711:227: tshe dang dngos grub bsgrub pa dang *//
NG0711:228: char pa dbab dang ser ba bzlog / thams cad rim par shes par bya //
NG0711:229: de yi gsang sngags 'di lta ste //
NG0711:230: om tsan+da ma ha ro sha nashan+ting ku ru hum phat /
NG0711:233: ma ra ya ra k+sha ku ru /
NG0711:234: om brum badzra a yu:she hum a /
NG0711:237: om na ga ka la hum /
NG0711:238: na ga le dum pa le le /
NG0711:240: om g+hi li g+hi la 'bar sha 'bar sha pa
NG0711:241: ta ya pa ta ya hum hum hum ho ho
NG0711:242: ho phat phat phat swa ha /
NG0711:243: ser ba u na ma ni phat swa ha /
NG0711:244: gtum po dbang bskur ba man ngag gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NG0711:245: las kha tshar gyi le'u ste brgyad pa'o ///
NG0711:246: / de nas dpal rdo rje gtum po la //
NG0711:247: 'khor rnams dges nas bstod pa ni /
NG0711:248: e ma ho rdo rje gtum po yis //
NG0711:249: gsang rgyas kun gyis dbang bskrur bas //
NG0711:250: sangs rgyas kun pas sngar sangs rgyas //
NG0711:251: khro rgyal de la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0711:253: mchod pas mnyes par byas par gyur to //
NG0711:254: gtum po gsang dbang bskur ba man ngag gi rgyud las /

NG0711:256: // // de nas khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil pas
NG0711:257: / bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0711:258: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje gtum nyid /

NG0711:261: rdo rje gtum pos bka' stsal pa /
NG0711:262: rgyud 'di rnal 'byor pa dam la gnas pa /
